title: FROTH: Origin Fields Adds ShockOne, The Veronicas, Cub Sport & More To Their NYE Lineup
text:
Thanks for signing up!

Origin Fields has just announced its second round of artists and, sweet Jesus, there are some fucking impression additions to an already-stellar lineup.

Tyler, The Creator, Skepta, RL Grime, Ella Mai, RÜFÜS DU SOL will now be joined by the likes of The Veronicas, Cub Sport, ShockOne, Blackbear, Monxx and Motez. ShockOne will also be performing his set with a live band for first time, which is a pretty bloody huge mood.

More acts are still to be announced, if you weren’t frothing hard enough already.

Check out the updated lineup below. For further lineup and ticket info, head on over to the official website. This NYE is shaping to be a big one.
